/div> <p><span>The Pacer Global Cash Cows Dividend ETF (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">BATS:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/GCOW\" title=\"Pacer Global Cash Cows Dividend ETF\">GCOW</a></span>), launched on 02/22/2016 and managed by Pacer Advisors, Inc., is an ETF that tracks the performance of the Pacer Global Cash Cows Dividend Index.</span></p> <p>There is a strong case</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1345912457/image_1345912457.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741430-gcow-an-international-dividend-fund-with-a-solid-track-record", "pub_date": "2024-12-02 08:41:30"}, {"id": "4741429", "title": "Auto Insurer Progressive Held Up In Traffic As Valuation Puts Brakes On Rating", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1829394152/image_1829394152.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Toy Car In Front Of Businessman Calculating Loan. Saving money for car concept, trade car for cash concept, finance concept.\" data-id=\"1829394152\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1829394152/image_1829394152.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1829394152/image_1829394152.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1829394152/image_1829394152.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1829394152/image_1829394152.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1829394152/image_1829394152.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1829394152/image_1829394152.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1829394152/image_1829394152.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https